blMSRbJ_childItem_9","default":"<p>What if the supplement doesn’t work for me?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_10","label":"gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_10","default":"<p>What is your return policy?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJ59b-ywE__text","label":"ggJ59b-ywE__text","default":"<p>No, SciatiCalm is only available online through our official website. This allows us to keep prices low and ensure product authenticity.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOF78_pLax_text","label":"ggOF78_pLax_text","default":"<p>Each serving contains:</p><ul><li>Organic Turmeric Root Powder – 900mg</li><li>Turmeric Root Extract (95% Standardized Curcuminoids) – 100mg</li><li>BioPerine® (Black Pepper Fruit Extract) – 7mg</li><li>All ingredients are encapsulated in a gelatin capsule.</li></ul>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGBgdMGN1b_text","label":"ggGBgdMGN1b_text","default":"<p>While SciatiCalm contains natural, well-tolerated ingredients, we always recommend consulting your doctor if you are currently taking prescription medications or have a medical condition.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5779-Q2LD_text","label":"gg5779-Q2LD_text","default":"<p>Keep the bottle in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Do not refrigerate. Always store out of reach of children.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrcqOh_tmz_text","label":"ggrcqOh_tmz_text","default":"<p>SciatiCalm is formulated to support nerve health, reduce inflammation, and promote myelin repair — all of which are important in managing sciatica and nerve-related discomfort. Many users report a noticeable reduction in pain, tingling, and burning sensations within weeks.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text","label":"ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text","default":"<p>Some users begin to notice reduced discomfort within 5–7 days. Most report significant improvement within 2–4 weeks, with continued benefits over 45–90 days of consistent use.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggT40bKuK75_text","label":"ggT40bKuK75_text","default":"<p>Take 3 capsules per day, ideally with food. Most users take all 3 in the morning or split the dose between breakfast and dinner.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRWVQP7xyG_text","label":"ggRWVQP7xyG_text","default":"<p>Each bottle contains 90 capsules — enough for 30 days when taken as directed.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5QWW06sGv_text","label":"gg5QWW06sGv_text","default":"<p>SciatiCalm is designed for adults. If you are pregnant, nursing, or under 18, consult a healthcare provider before use. It is generally safe for seniors when taken as directed.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghn7pMgHJ7_text","label":"gghn7pMgHJ7_text","default":"<p>We stand behind SciatiCalm with a 90-day money-back guarantee. If you’re not satisfied for any reason, simply contact us and we’ll refund your order — no hassle, no questions asked.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzmHVH4LpH_text","label":"ggzmHVH4LpH_text","default":"<p>Every order is backed by our 90-day risk-free guarantee. If you’re not happy with your results, return the product (even empty bottles) within 90 days for a full refund.</p>"}],
